commitMessage: introducing main layout above GameView.
dont use new Long() constructor
Correct lint warnings.
* Fixed a bug where switching back and forth between two days would desync date in header and the true menu date. * A bit of cleaning up in HttpMultipartClient
FIXED: #re-use view if already exists, this will increase performance a little
BUGFIX: Recycle views to scroll faster

The bus times fetching and Twitter feed fetching tasks have now been partially rewritten as AsyncTask tasks which should aid in code maintainability. The bus stop map can now accept stop codes in the calling Intent for zooming in to a particular stop. DisplayStopDataActivity now shows how long it has been since the last data refresh... which addresses a feature request and closes issue 16. FavouriteStopsActivity now shows a list of bus services for each saved stop and now lets users zoom to that stop on the map in the context menu. The preferences have been reordered for more logical ordering. Added a user preference where the user can elect to show the list of favourite bus stops on application start up rather than the menu. Modified a few of the custom list adapters to use convertView for faster layout drawing. NearestStopsActivity now uses some helpful hints found at http://android-developers.blogspot.com/2011/06/deep-dive-into-location.html
